title: Brennessel Naturkostladen
description: Well-stocked mini market and health food shop in the small part of Kiel called Pries. Offers only organic products including fresh bread, spreads, raw food snacks, soya milk, oat and rice drinks, tofu, miso, wakame, cereals, gluten free food, coffee, chocolate, biscuits, juices, cosmetics and personal care products, ecological cleaning products and supplements.
